  "title": "*New* Videographer / Video Content Creator / Video Editor (Office Hours, 5 Days) #HJG",
  "description": "<h2>Job Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Assist in content development and creation for marketing and outreach initiatives across digital and print platforms</p></li><li><p>Support the production of visual and promotional materials, including basic photo and video content</p></li><li><p>Perform basic video recording, stitching, and editing using Adobe software</p></li><li><p>Assist with website content updates and coordination of marketing materials</p></li><li><p>Support event coordination and outreach activities</p></li><li><p>Carry out administrative duties, including data collation, documentation, and coordination work</p></li><li><p>Provide administrative and coordination support during the Training Grant evaluation phase</p></li></ul><h2>Job Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Min GCE N/O or ‘A’ Levels / Diploma and above</p></li><li><p>No experience needed, full training will be provided</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of Microsoft Office</p></li><li><p>Able to start work immediately</p></li></ul><p>If you are interested in this position, do kindly drop your most updated resume to <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">joshua.gan@recruitexpress.com.sg</a> and <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">leonleong@recruitexpress.com.sg</a> (Attn: Videographer)</p><p>Leon Leong De Cong<br />R1551708<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifesciences Division)<br />EA License: 99C4599</p>",
